snippet.title: Movie Game Challenge Trailer
snippet.description:
The Movie Game Challenge is a new iOS Game available on the App Store.  tests users film knowledge by using the cast members and actors careers to connect films and actors together.

Available at the App Store: https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/movie-game-challenge/id1454323501?ls=1&mt=8
